Traineeship Description:
This position reports to the Sales Director and interfaces with company managers and staff. SIMTRUM is a venture-funded, e-commerce business in the photonics industries that is disrupting the traditional retail and ecommerce business models using an innovative, hybrid commerce approach. The company boasts of an unmatched team with well-known names from technology, global consumer brands and retail. At the core, it is a young-minded company with a great, flexible working environment, respect for individual and team contribution, and a zeal for achieving the impossible.

Specific Responsibilities:
Trainee to be involved in:
 Assist product manager to developed particular product line and prepare the product specification drawing, application note etc.
 Establishing product pricing strategy by analyzing key competitor뭩 price and company channel strategy
 Establish relationship with supply chain, understand supply chain뭩 capability and integrate those product into our product portfolio
 Advance product development methodology, policies to improve and enhance user experience, product and feature prioritization, release predictability, quality, and velocity
 Design and outsource product packaging for assigned product line
Assist product manager to alliance with supplier for product information, stock level, and quality control document etc.

Technical Skills and Competencies Trainee will learn during SGUnited Traineeship Programme:
 Creativity &amp; problem solving
 Research &amp; analytics skills
 Product development &amp; planning skills
. Physics , engineering, photonics knowledge